ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0439728 | title=The Netherbeast of Berm-Tech Industries, Inc. | publisher=IMDB | accessdate=18 July 2019}}</ref>\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''The Inevitable Reggie Vandervan''<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1391542 | title=The Inevitable Reggie Vandervan | publisher=IMDB | accessdate=18 July 2019}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''Sick Day''<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0378761 | title=Sick Day | publisher=IMDB | accessdate=18 July 2019}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''The Strange Case of Ray Milland''<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0460574 | title=The Strange Case of Ray Milland | publisher=IMDB | accessdate=18 July 2019}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''A. Lincoln: A Life Embellished''<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0434761 | title=A. Lincoln: A Life Embellished | publisher=IMDB | accessdate=18 July 2019}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|1782510}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dellis, Bruce}}\n[[Category:American male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:People from Tempe, Arizona]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Film directors from Arizona]]\n[[Category:Screenwriters from Arizona]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{US-film-director-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{BLP sources|date=July 2010}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Bruce Dellis\n| image              =\n| caption            = Dellis on the set of Raising Buchanan\n| birth_name         = Bruce Dellis\n| home_town           = [[Tempe, Arizona]], U.S.\n| occupation         = Film director and screenwriter\n| years_active       = 2003\u2013present\n| spouse             = {{marriage|Connie Dellis|1990}}\n| children           = 1\n}}\n\n'''Bruce Dellis''' is an American [[film direc